A980520.zip is a zip file containing the sources for an OTI Smalltalk
implementation of the Cassowary solver.  The kernel classes are all in the
ClKernel application.  There are a few examples of the programmer interface
to the solver in ClTests, and some graphical demonstrations in ClDemos.

To run the demos evaluate the following after the code has been loaded:


(ClBinaryTreeDemo height: 5)  open.
ClBoxesDemo new open.
ClElasticQuadDemo new open.
ClBoundedQuadDemo new open.
ClQuadDemo new open.

